lead_paragraph: DeMar DeRozan scored 27 points, Kyle Lowry added 22, and Toronto Raptors held off the Memphis Grizzlies for a 99-95 victory on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: DeRozan, Lowry Lead Raptors Past Grizzlies 99-95
